Constructor Detail

GP

public GP(PosNegLP learningProblem,
          ReasoningService rs)
Creates an algorithm object. By default a steady state algorithm with rank selection is used. This operates on a population of 1000 individuals with a probability of crossover of 1.0 and a probability of mutation of 0.01.
